divs: Sighting Detailsi was sitting typing on a laptop at my mothers house as it is in front of the window, i happend to look out and noticed a small rainbow just above the satelite dish that is on the wall opposite i thought this was unusual in it`s self so i took a picture with my phone as this was all i had to hand. then when i viewed the picture to my amazement there was a large glowing orb. which i could not see when looking out of the window.
